This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the segmentation of histology images. The use of deep learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of "hierarchical architecture" and "multi-level contextual features" suggests that it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of "multi-task learning" suggests that it could belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
